title: Best Bits of the Week with Morgan2 - 'What You Didn't Hear About Raymundo's Wedding' Week of 10/26
itunes:title: Best Bits of the Week with Morgan2 - 'What You Didn't Hear About Raymundo's Wedding' Week of 10/26
description:
Morgan2 recaps the biggest 7 segments from The Bobby Bones Show every week. This podcast features behind the scenes a from show members and moments that happened after we turned off the microphones. Morgan2 brings in Amy, Raymundo, Eddie and Lunchbox this week to talk about stories they didn't get to share on air.
